Today is the day we say the goodbye we never got too. I miss you more as everyday passes . The short time I had you in my life I learned more about who I am and who I want to be. Thank you for reminding me my worth and to keep pushing for my goals. I love you brother see you on the other side .

About a year ago I reconnected with someone who I always had amazing chemistry with and decided to give it a shot .After not seeing each other in over 10 years we picked up right where we left off . 9 months ago I asked her to be my girlfriend and made her a promise to build a life together with her and her amazing boys. Today we live together in a beautiful home and both boys are making huge strides and improving in many areas. This Easter I am so thankful to have my amazing little family. I am so glad this beautiful woman took a chance on me. I know not everyday is easy to deal with me but she does an amazing job and I am blessed. Happy 9 months babe I look forward to growing stronger every day with you . #Purple@Gold #forever@always
